official_title: Imagio Feasibility Multi-Reader, Multi-Case Study of Optoacoustic Images Versus Imagio Ultrasound to Guide Decision to Biopsy
inclusion_criteria:
- Female subjects participating in the PIONEER-0 Study of the Imagio Breast Imaging System with known clinical status
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must be FEMALE
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
exclusion_criteria: - Female subjects who did not have known clinical status in the PIONEER-0 Study of the Imagio Breast Imaging System with known clinical status
